WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:05.400


00:00:07.721 --> 00:00:09.481
[If you don't turn yourself in,
your limbs will rot and you'll die]

00:00:37.938 --> 00:00:41.338
[All characters and events are fictional,
and any resemblance is coincidental]

00:00:41.338 --> 00:00:43.972
[Scenes with children and animals were filmed
safely under professional supervision]

00:00:43.972 --> 00:00:47.105
[Establishing Law and Order]
Mr. Lee Yong Woo, have you been well?

00:00:47.105 --> 00:00:49.938
[Compliance Required]
Why didn't you come yesterday?

00:00:49.938 --> 00:00:53.005
Something urgent came up.

00:00:53.005 --> 00:00:55.972
Were you waiting for me?

00:00:55.972 --> 00:00:57.449
Something urgent?

00:00:57.449 --> 00:00:58.601
[Confession is the beginning of forgiveness,
and forgiveness opens the door to salvation]

00:00:58.601 --> 00:01:01.338
Guess this isn't all that urgent to you.

00:01:01.338 --> 00:01:02.938
Well, why would it be?

00:01:02.938 --> 00:01:06.372
The statute of limitations
has already expired anyway.

00:01:06.372 --> 00:01:09.638
Right, nothing urgent about it.

00:01:09.638 --> 00:01:13.138
The more important something is,
the less you should rush it.

00:01:13.138 --> 00:01:14.772
Important?

00:01:14.772 --> 00:01:16.809
This is

00:01:16.809 --> 00:01:19.372
like my life's mission.

00:01:20.338 --> 00:01:22.572
"Mission", huh?

00:01:22.572 --> 00:01:24.172
Sounds impressive.

00:01:25.072 --> 00:01:26.505
What do you mean?

00:01:26.505 --> 00:01:28.538
A life's mission?

00:01:28.538 --> 00:01:31.005
People like me don't have anything like that.

00:01:31.005 --> 00:01:35.872
How did you end up getting into that,

00:01:35.872 --> 00:01:38.238
your life's mission?

00:01:44.138 --> 00:01:46.738
What got me started?

00:01:53.872 --> 00:01:56.938
Calling won't wake her up.

00:01:56.938 --> 00:01:58.838
Go get questioned.

00:01:58.838 --> 00:01:59.872
On what?

00:01:59.872 --> 00:02:00.872
[Episode 3]

00:02:00.872 --> 00:02:04.638
The assault on Jeon Kyeong Ho.
That's my jurisdiction.

00:02:08.172 --> 00:02:11.472
Are you seriously
going to lock me up over that?

00:02:12.073 --> 00:02:16.005
You think the case is going
to be handed to you now?

00:02:17.038 --> 00:02:19.238
It's already mine.

00:02:19.905 --> 00:02:20.905
What?

00:02:20.905 --> 00:02:22.738
I told you.

00:02:22.738 --> 00:02:25.005
I'd take it back.

00:02:25.005 --> 00:02:26.313
You,

00:02:26.313 --> 00:02:27.938
and the case.

00:02:31.205 --> 00:02:33.038
Hey.

00:02:33.038 --> 00:02:36.972
Forget about petty things
like asking to make a phone call.

00:02:36.972 --> 00:02:39.138
Just for once,

00:02:39.138 --> 00:02:42.371
say, "Please help me."

00:02:42.371 --> 00:02:43.405
Jeez.

00:02:43.405 --> 00:02:46.072
Then I'll take care of everything.

00:02:57.238 --> 00:02:58.627
Tae Joo.

00:02:59.472 --> 00:03:01.105
Kang Tae Joo.

00:03:03.172 --> 00:03:04.649
We can

00:03:04.649 --> 00:03:06.638
take that punk down together.

00:03:08.872 --> 00:03:10.972
You and me, we do this together.

00:03:23.905 --> 00:03:25.605
Didn't I already tell you?

00:03:26.305 --> 00:03:28.041
Cut the "we" crap.

00:03:28.041 --> 00:03:30.905
I don't want anything to do with you.

00:03:33.272 --> 00:03:35.972
You're gonna help me?

00:03:37.005 --> 00:03:38.672
You?

00:03:40.305 --> 00:03:42.438
What a joke.

00:03:43.172 --> 00:03:44.638
Prosecutor Cha Si Young.

00:03:44.638 --> 00:03:47.505
You really wanna help me?

00:03:47.505 --> 00:03:49.405
Get your face

00:03:49.405 --> 00:03:51.572
out of my sight.

00:03:57.438 --> 00:04:00.138
If that's what you want, fine.

00:04:05.072 --> 00:04:09.972
[Police officer arrested]
The victim needs eight weeks to recover.

00:04:09.972 --> 00:04:11.805
What are you going to do about this?

00:04:13.872 --> 00:04:15.593
Is there

00:04:15.593 --> 00:04:18.838
any way to handle this quietly?

00:04:20.905 --> 00:04:25.238
I even considered indicting him immediately,

00:04:25.238 --> 00:04:29.405
but with the recent serial murders,
public trust in the police is at rock bottom.

00:04:29.405 --> 00:04:31.872
It just didn't feel right.

00:04:33.005 --> 00:04:34.638
That's right.

00:04:36.838 --> 00:04:39.838
Let's just take his resignation
quietly and end it.

00:04:40.972 --> 00:04:44.038
Yeah, that sounds best.

00:04:44.038 --> 00:04:45.772
- Do that.
- Chief!

00:04:45.772 --> 00:04:47.805
You still don't get it even now?

00:04:47.805 --> 00:04:50.172
Eight weeks means jail time, no question.

00:04:50.172 --> 00:04:52.505
And jail time means dismissal anyway.

00:04:55.272 --> 00:04:56.338
Why aren't you answering?

00:04:56.338 --> 00:04:58.872
Please have Detective Kang questioned.

00:04:58.872 --> 00:04:59.972
What?

00:04:59.972 --> 00:05:01.505
He's still a police officer.

00:05:01.505 --> 00:05:04.072
He even saved a woman
from the suspect this time.

00:05:04.072 --> 00:05:06.305
So you're asking me to let him off?

00:05:06.305 --> 00:05:07.838
No, what I mean is

00:05:07.838 --> 00:05:10.838
he's done his job properly
for over ten years.

00:05:10.838 --> 00:05:14.205
If you throw someone like that out,
morale among the others will drop.

00:05:14.205 --> 00:05:18.238
Chief, honestly,
who'd even want to be a cop then?

00:05:18.972 --> 00:05:20.738
Please show some leniency.

00:05:25.105 --> 00:05:27.438
Fine, let's do that.

00:05:27.438 --> 00:05:31.272
If it makes you uncomfortable
to fire your colleague,

00:05:31.272 --> 00:05:32.605
what can we do?

00:05:32.605 --> 00:05:34.705
Just follow procedure.

00:05:35.572 --> 00:05:39.238
Anyway, Detective Kang Tae Joo is removed
from all investigations, effective today.

00:05:39.238 --> 00:05:40.938
Procedure followed.

00:05:57.091 --> 00:05:58.307
[Seo Ji Won]

00:05:59.938 --> 00:06:02.472
Sun Young, why are you here?

00:06:07.138 --> 00:06:09.205
How's Ji Won?

00:06:09.205 --> 00:06:10.405
Still unconscious?

00:06:10.405 --> 00:06:12.038
I heard

00:06:12.672 --> 00:06:15.205
she got hurt
trying to catch the suspect with you.

00:06:19.305 --> 00:06:21.472
Seriously,

00:06:21.472 --> 00:06:23.738
it's always about that darn suspect.

00:06:23.738 --> 00:06:26.505
Why are you only here now?
Where were you back then?

00:06:28.772 --> 00:06:30.838
Were you chasing the suspect again?

00:06:32.672 --> 00:06:34.972
Come out for a second.

00:06:40.838 --> 00:06:43.049
Kang Sun Young, first,

00:06:43.049 --> 00:06:45.272
explain what happened to you.

00:06:45.272 --> 00:06:50.038
Why were you in the car with him?
And why did he do that to you?

00:06:51.572 --> 00:06:53.801
Shouldn't you

00:06:53.801 --> 00:06:55.238
ask if I'm okay first?

00:06:55.238 --> 00:06:57.172
What's your relationship with that punk?

00:07:02.172 --> 00:07:04.205
A student got into a car accident.

00:07:04.205 --> 00:07:06.805
So I went to the hospital with him,

00:07:06.805 --> 00:07:09.838
and he offered to give me a ride home,
so I just got in.

00:07:09.838 --> 00:07:11.568
Then

00:07:11.568 --> 00:07:13.505
how does he know about our mother?

00:07:13.505 --> 00:07:15.738
You think I told him?

00:07:16.705 --> 00:07:20.905
He suddenly started saying weird things,
so I asked to get out, but he got angry.

00:07:20.905 --> 00:07:23.005
And then, the accident happened.

00:07:26.238 --> 00:07:29.238
Did that guy do anything to you?

00:07:29.238 --> 00:07:31.138
No, nothing like that happened.

00:07:32.705 --> 00:07:35.938
Jeez, that woman really is something.

00:07:35.938 --> 00:07:39.105
Even in death, she's dragging her kids down.

00:07:40.738 --> 00:07:43.072
Don't talk about her like that.

00:07:43.072 --> 00:07:45.872
Mom did her best for us.

00:07:46.538 --> 00:07:48.505
Best?

00:07:48.505 --> 00:07:50.738
You call that the best?

00:07:50.738 --> 00:07:54.072
That woman left you when you were sick
and went off with another man.

00:07:54.072 --> 00:07:56.638
- You don't know what you're talking about!
- Tae Joo, stop!

00:08:43.205 --> 00:08:46.105
Sun Young, just hang in there
a little longer.

00:09:08.372 --> 00:09:09.972
Sorry.

00:09:23.172 --> 00:09:25.872
He told me to apply for a transfer.

00:09:27.605 --> 00:09:30.605
He kept threatening me with my son,

00:09:30.605 --> 00:09:32.572
so I had no choice.

00:09:33.805 --> 00:09:35.738
Yeah, I see.

00:09:37.372 --> 00:09:38.953
It was

00:09:38.953 --> 00:09:40.905
about seven years ago?

00:09:40.905 --> 00:09:42.435
Everyone from the office

00:09:42.435 --> 00:09:44.972
went on a company outing.

00:09:46.605 --> 00:09:48.361
Back then,

00:09:48.361 --> 00:09:50.438
Mr. Cha, who didn't even have kids,

00:09:50.438 --> 00:09:53.838
got along so well with my son.

00:09:56.572 --> 00:09:59.605
He treated him like his own nephew.

00:09:59.605 --> 00:10:01.438
But

00:10:02.405 --> 00:10:05.505
he'd even torture my son mercilessly.

00:10:05.505 --> 00:10:07.472
Is that punk even human?

00:10:13.672 --> 00:10:15.625
Jeez,

00:10:15.625 --> 00:10:18.338
I've been talking too much about myself.

00:10:18.338 --> 00:10:21.038
You must have
a lot on your mind too, Detective Kang.

00:10:21.038 --> 00:10:22.672
No, it's all right.

00:10:23.572 --> 00:10:26.205
Isn't it ironic?

00:10:26.205 --> 00:10:28.713
We're the ones who drove out Cha Si Young,

00:10:28.713 --> 00:10:31.138
and now we are in trouble.

00:10:35.505 --> 00:10:37.138
It's probably just a coincidence.

00:10:37.138 --> 00:10:39.372
Do you really think so?

00:10:40.805 --> 00:10:42.889
Cha Si Young

00:10:42.889 --> 00:10:45.238
is a horrible man.

00:10:45.238 --> 00:10:48.638
He'll use any means to get what he wants.

00:10:48.638 --> 00:10:51.805
Try not to go up against him if you can.

00:10:51.805 --> 00:10:53.737
Otherwise,

00:10:53.737 --> 00:10:55.972
the one who'll get hurt
is you, Detective Kang.

00:10:59.105 --> 00:11:01.538
Don't worry about me.

00:11:01.538 --> 00:11:03.538
I don't care

00:11:04.572 --> 00:11:06.638
about means or methods, either.

00:11:10.772 --> 00:11:15.705
[Modako]

00:11:15.705 --> 00:11:17.572
Welcome!

00:11:17.572 --> 00:11:20.438
It's an honor to have someone
as distinguished as you here.

00:11:21.638 --> 00:11:22.838
This way, please.

00:11:22.838 --> 00:11:24.538
Yes, this way.

00:11:36.672 --> 00:11:38.305
Here.

00:11:41.438 --> 00:11:44.105
If I get caught, I'm dead.

00:11:45.272 --> 00:11:47.938
Let's call your debt to me even with this.

00:11:52.405 --> 00:11:54.472
Which one of those two?

00:11:56.238 --> 00:11:58.072
Both of those punks.

00:12:02.305 --> 00:12:05.072
Please visit us often.

00:12:07.072 --> 00:12:10.172
[Modako Club VIP Pass]

00:12:10.172 --> 00:12:12.738
Bring another glass here.

00:12:12.738 --> 00:12:14.372
Hey!

00:12:17.673 --> 00:12:21.005
Alright, you guys talk.

00:12:22.138 --> 00:12:26.057
You're such a decent man.

00:12:26.057 --> 00:12:28.205
So you must've been shocked.

00:12:32.072 --> 00:12:34.938
So, what about that punk?

00:12:34.938 --> 00:12:37.438
We can throw him in jail, right?

00:12:37.438 --> 00:12:39.772
Of course, that's nothing.

00:12:40.969 --> 00:12:46.838
But I heard that woman filed
a complaint against me. How do we...

00:12:48.572 --> 00:12:52.505
That's why I'm asking.
Why did you hit a woman?

00:12:52.505 --> 00:12:56.105
I'm sorry. I just lost it in anger
before I knew it.

00:12:56.838 --> 00:12:58.905
Then there's no other way.

00:12:58.905 --> 00:13:01.105
You'll have to admit
you were having an affair.

00:13:01.105 --> 00:13:02.905
What? An affair?

00:13:02.905 --> 00:13:06.505
Your mistress, Kang Sun Young
has been demanding you get a divorce,

00:13:06.505 --> 00:13:08.672
but you refused to do it.

00:13:08.672 --> 00:13:11.605
So during an argument,
things escalated into an accident.

00:13:11.605 --> 00:13:15.972
Now, holding a grudge,
she's claiming you assaulted her.

00:13:16.838 --> 00:13:19.272
But my wife's going to kill me.

00:13:20.338 --> 00:13:23.705
Sir, you really don't understand women.

00:13:25.005 --> 00:13:27.005
She won't kill you.

00:13:36.505 --> 00:13:41.838
Jeez, your back always acts up like this.
What should we do?

00:13:41.838 --> 00:13:45.005
When you get old,
everything just starts breaking down.

00:13:45.005 --> 00:13:48.438
First you fooled around
with a married man, now what?

00:13:48.438 --> 00:13:50.805
You tried to replace me, his lawful wife?

00:13:50.805 --> 00:13:54.972
How can you even call yourself a teacher?

00:13:54.972 --> 00:13:57.572
What are you talking about? Let go!

00:13:57.572 --> 00:13:59.705
Don't you dare deny it!

00:13:59.705 --> 00:14:03.572
You're the daughter of a bar hostess.
No wonder you act the same.

00:14:03.572 --> 00:14:05.838
What else would you have learned?

00:14:05.838 --> 00:14:08.238
She's the daughter of a bar hostess?

00:14:12.705 --> 00:14:14.972
Sun Young!

00:14:15.705 --> 00:14:17.805
Oh my, Sun Young!

00:14:17.805 --> 00:14:19.872
What's all this about?

00:14:19.872 --> 00:14:21.605
What are you doing?

00:14:21.605 --> 00:14:23.905
What? Why?

00:14:23.905 --> 00:14:27.238
Can't I do this much to the mistress
who slept with my husband?

00:14:27.238 --> 00:14:28.305
W-What?

00:14:28.305 --> 00:14:30.505
She's a bar hostess' daughter.

00:14:31.395 --> 00:14:33.938
No...

00:14:33.938 --> 00:14:37.038
Mother, it's not true.

00:14:37.038 --> 00:14:38.372
It's not true, Mother.

00:14:38.372 --> 00:14:40.472
It's really not true.

00:14:41.305 --> 00:14:44.138
Mother?

00:14:44.138 --> 00:14:45.705
Oh dear, Mother!

00:14:45.705 --> 00:14:47.372
You've got such a fine daughter-in-law.

00:14:47.372 --> 00:14:49.672
Oh my, isn't she impressive?

00:14:49.672 --> 00:14:53.105
Mother, it's not true.

00:14:57.205 --> 00:14:59.805
Mother, I swear it's not true.

00:15:02.872 --> 00:15:05.638
Break up with Ki Beom.

00:15:06.838 --> 00:15:08.438
Mother...

00:15:08.438 --> 00:15:12.505
They say a woman's fate
takes after her mother's.

00:15:12.505 --> 00:15:14.872
I shouldn't just brush it off.

00:15:15.772 --> 00:15:18.972
Mother, what she said earlier isn't true.

00:15:18.972 --> 00:15:20.672
Please believe me.

00:15:21.838 --> 00:15:23.705
Your mother was like that too.

00:15:23.705 --> 00:15:27.105
Men flocked to her even when she did nothing.

00:15:27.105 --> 00:15:31.638
She didn't live like that from the beginning.

00:15:31.638 --> 00:15:33.738
After your father passed away,

00:15:33.738 --> 00:15:37.672
she had to raise you somehow,
so that's how it ended up.

00:15:40.038 --> 00:15:42.338
I'm afraid

00:15:42.338 --> 00:15:46.972
you might even take after her
in bringing misfortune to your husband.

00:15:46.972 --> 00:15:49.638
That's what scares me the most.

00:15:56.638 --> 00:15:58.472
Sun Young.

00:16:01.905 --> 00:16:05.272
Please let Ki Beom go.

00:16:05.272 --> 00:16:08.172
I'm begging you, okay?

00:16:17.505 --> 00:16:23.638
[Kangseng Bookstore]

00:16:23.638 --> 00:16:27.572
[Muwon Photo Studio]

00:16:29.005 --> 00:16:32.105
Sun Young would look beautiful
in a wedding dress too.

00:16:32.105 --> 00:16:34.905
Sun Young will stay
at a relative's place for a while.

00:16:34.905 --> 00:16:37.105
Nothing's wrong, I hope.

00:16:41.283 --> 00:16:42.772
Sir, this way.

00:16:42.772 --> 00:16:44.305
Oh, you're totally wasted.

00:16:44.305 --> 00:16:45.838
How come you can hold your liquor so well?

00:16:45.838 --> 00:16:48.772
Of course, I can.

00:16:48.772 --> 00:16:49.938
Hey, wait, wait.

00:16:49.938 --> 00:16:51.105
Stop right there.

00:16:51.105 --> 00:16:53.905
Hey, wait. I'm paying today!

00:16:53.905 --> 00:16:56.838
Alright.

00:16:56.838 --> 00:16:58.569
Right here.

00:16:58.569 --> 00:17:00.937
Darn it. Alright.

00:17:01.672 --> 00:17:03.405
Here.

00:17:03.405 --> 00:17:05.672
[Modako Club VIP Pass]

00:17:06.538 --> 00:17:08.172
Thank you!

00:17:10.805 --> 00:17:12.605
Here.

00:17:12.605 --> 00:17:14.205
Thank you, sir!

00:17:15.338 --> 00:17:16.672
You're really generous!

00:17:16.672 --> 00:17:19.438
Hey, what's your boss doing?

00:17:19.438 --> 00:17:22.172
The guests are leaving.

00:17:22.172 --> 00:17:24.672
Hey, why the boss?

00:17:24.672 --> 00:17:28.072
Oh, it's fine, man.
I'm close with the owner here.

00:17:28.072 --> 00:17:29.505
Oh, really?

00:17:29.505 --> 00:17:31.872
Go call him over!

00:17:31.872 --> 00:17:33.638
- Go call him right away!
- Yes, sir.

00:17:33.638 --> 00:17:35.205
Mr. Park!

00:17:35.205 --> 00:17:38.038
Oh my, Mr. Jeon!

00:17:38.038 --> 00:17:40.605
Is everything alright here?

00:17:40.605 --> 00:17:43.338
Good, good.

00:17:43.338 --> 00:17:48.072
Thanks to you, Mr. Park,
I had a great time again today!

00:17:48.872 --> 00:17:51.572
I'm leaving!

00:17:51.572 --> 00:17:54.605
- Bye, sir!
- Goodbye, sir.

00:17:54.605 --> 00:17:57.005
I'll be back tomorrow too.

00:17:57.005 --> 00:17:58.305
See you again.

00:17:58.305 --> 00:18:00.738
Come again, sir!

00:18:00.738 --> 00:18:04.472
Is that punk out of his mind?

00:18:12.938 --> 00:18:15.805
That nephew of the county governor

00:18:15.805 --> 00:18:18.538
is basically living here for free booze.

00:18:18.538 --> 00:18:20.638
Anyway, rich people are always the worst.

00:18:20.638 --> 00:18:23.638
How long do we have to keep babying him?

00:18:23.638 --> 00:18:26.405
Cleaning up after him is one thing,
but this is too much.

00:18:26.405 --> 00:18:28.238
Cleaning up what?

00:18:30.505 --> 00:18:32.238
I mean...

00:18:33.038 --> 00:18:35.105
I'm the boss here,

00:18:35.105 --> 00:18:37.505
and that punk acting out
in front of everyone...

00:18:38.172 --> 00:18:40.805
It's embarrassing even
for my employees to see.

00:18:46.805 --> 00:18:48.672
Darn it.

00:18:49.405 --> 00:18:51.505
Why does the booze taste like this?

00:18:51.505 --> 00:18:52.638
Are you still watering it down?

00:18:52.638 --> 00:18:54.405
No way!

00:18:54.405 --> 00:18:57.405
Since I got suspended back then,
I've never done that again.

00:18:57.405 --> 00:18:59.738
With all the customers
you've introduced to me,

00:18:59.738 --> 00:19:02.538
do you really think I'd disgrace you?

00:19:02.538 --> 00:19:05.172
- Really?
- Of course.

00:19:06.172 --> 00:19:08.405
Does it not suit your taste?

00:19:10.038 --> 00:19:13.605
Hold on. I'll bring you something else.

00:19:50.438 --> 00:19:52.805
Si Young, what about this?

00:19:52.805 --> 00:19:55.305
The most expensive bottle we've got...

00:20:00.872 --> 00:20:03.105
You little...

00:20:05.972 --> 00:20:07.605
What the hell is this?

00:20:09.238 --> 00:20:11.472
Are you bugging me?

00:20:11.472 --> 00:20:12.672
How dare you!

00:20:12.672 --> 00:20:14.305
It wasn't me.

00:20:15.672 --> 00:20:18.772
It's a misunderstanding. I swear!

00:20:19.538 --> 00:20:21.438
Not you?

00:20:21.438 --> 00:20:22.805
Get lost.

00:20:22.805 --> 00:20:24.438
Yes, sir.

00:20:30.538 --> 00:20:32.073
Si Young,

00:20:32.073 --> 00:20:33.872
why would I...

00:20:34.605 --> 00:20:38.005
Believe me, it really wasn't me!

00:20:39.572 --> 00:20:41.405
Prove it.

00:20:42.672 --> 00:20:46.472
Fine, I'll prove it. I'll prove it!

00:21:08.238 --> 00:21:09.872
Oh, my head.

00:21:12.131 --> 00:21:13.769
Gosh.

00:21:24.072 --> 00:21:25.772
- Ji Won.
- Yeah.

00:21:25.772 --> 00:21:27.072
Are you feeling a little clearer?

00:21:27.072 --> 00:21:29.205
What's wrong with my head?

00:21:30.172 --> 00:21:31.753
More importantly,

00:21:31.753 --> 00:21:33.838
did they catch the suspect?

00:21:33.838 --> 00:21:35.405
Is that what really matters right now?

00:21:35.405 --> 00:21:37.905
Did they catch him or not?

00:21:37.905 --> 00:21:38.938
Not yet.

00:21:38.938 --> 00:21:40.072
Darn it!

00:21:40.072 --> 00:21:42.272
Seriously? That's what you're asking
after a narrow escape?

00:21:42.272 --> 00:21:44.338
The camera!

00:21:44.338 --> 00:21:46.738
Did you find my camera?

00:21:46.738 --> 00:21:48.472
What camera?

00:21:48.472 --> 00:21:50.605
You didn't find it?

00:21:58.738 --> 00:22:01.172
Un Hui, is this even the right place?

00:22:01.172 --> 00:22:03.972
I checked with Mr. Park,
and he said it was here.

00:22:03.972 --> 00:22:05.705
Then why isn't the camera here?

00:22:05.705 --> 00:22:07.072
It's not like it can sink into the ground.

00:22:07.072 --> 00:22:09.738
Maybe the suspect took it?

00:22:09.738 --> 00:22:10.805
Think about it.

00:22:10.805 --> 00:22:13.372
Since it had captured him, do you think
he would've just left it behind?

00:22:13.372 --> 00:22:16.472
Darn it, we can't lose that.
That would have been a scoop.

00:22:18.172 --> 00:22:21.338
[Modako]

00:22:33.572 --> 00:22:36.105
Huh? Where did it go?

00:22:39.738 --> 00:22:41.338
Where is it?

00:22:43.171 --> 00:22:44.845
Jeez.

00:22:46.205 --> 00:22:48.005
What are you doing?

00:22:52.472 --> 00:22:54.372
Looking for this?

00:22:59.905 --> 00:23:02.138
Got you, you rat!

00:23:04.705 --> 00:23:06.338
So?

00:23:07.638 --> 00:23:09.238
What?

00:23:10.738 --> 00:23:12.338
Who?

00:23:15.105 --> 00:23:16.705
Got it.

00:23:24.805 --> 00:23:26.572
This is interesting.

00:23:29.938 --> 00:23:31.572
Very interesting.

00:23:32.338 --> 00:23:36.105
[The suspect's features]

00:23:36.105 --> 00:23:41.038
Do you remember anything else
about the suspect's features?

00:23:41.038 --> 00:23:44.072
Is it okay to just let him do this?

00:23:44.072 --> 00:23:46.005
Prosecutor Cha will go crazy if he finds out.

00:23:46.005 --> 00:23:47.038
Leave him be.

00:23:47.038 --> 00:23:49.405
[Body type, any weapons used]
He's trying so hard to catch the suspect.

00:23:49.405 --> 00:23:52.438
I think I already told you
everything that day.

00:23:52.438 --> 00:23:54.105
I didn't see his face.

00:23:54.105 --> 00:23:56.705
I told you everything I could remember

00:23:56.705 --> 00:23:59.538
about his height, build, and voice.

00:24:00.838 --> 00:24:03.238
Sorry for calling you in again.

00:24:03.238 --> 00:24:04.638
[The suspect's...]
Anything else coming to mind?

00:24:04.638 --> 00:24:06.405
No.

00:24:06.405 --> 00:24:08.705
Honestly, I don't even
want to think about it.

00:24:08.705 --> 00:24:11.638
Yes, I completely understand.

00:24:11.638 --> 00:24:13.272
[The suspect's last words]

00:24:13.272 --> 00:24:16.205
Then, just a few more questions.

00:24:16.205 --> 00:24:18.138
Ms. Kim Mi Yeon, when the suspect left you,

00:24:18.138 --> 00:24:20.305
what did he say before he left?

00:24:20.305 --> 00:24:23.505
Couldn't he just ask me directly?

00:24:25.605 --> 00:24:28.405
It's just that our situation
is a bit complicated.

00:24:28.405 --> 00:24:30.472
I'm sorry.

00:24:30.472 --> 00:24:34.305
He said if he caught that woman,
he'd let me go.

00:24:34.305 --> 00:24:39.472
But would a man who killed five people
really let me live?

00:24:39.472 --> 00:24:41.638
Five?

00:24:41.638 --> 00:24:42.805
What do you mean, five?

00:24:42.805 --> 00:24:47.105
He said he killed five people.

00:24:47.105 --> 00:24:50.405
What exactly did the suspect say?

00:24:51.107 --> 00:24:52.617
Well...

00:25:02.872 --> 00:25:05.005
See that woman?

00:25:05.005 --> 00:25:08.138
Once I catch her, I'll let you go.

00:25:08.138 --> 00:25:09.598
How about it?

00:25:09.598 --> 00:25:11.572
Will you cooperate?

00:25:20.705 --> 00:25:22.505
Don't try anything stupid.

00:25:22.505 --> 00:25:24.538
I've killed five women.

00:25:24.538 --> 00:25:26.372
Killing one more

00:25:26.372 --> 00:25:28.172
is nothing.

00:25:28.172 --> 00:25:29.672
Hey, what the...

00:25:29.672 --> 00:25:31.038
He said five?

00:25:31.038 --> 00:25:32.272
Maybe that punk got it wrong?

00:25:32.272 --> 00:25:34.038
He wouldn't be mistaken
about something like that.

00:25:34.038 --> 00:25:36.805
Then, if there's one more victim,
why hasn't the body been found yet?

00:25:38.238 --> 00:25:40.272
- A missing person!
- A missing person!

00:25:40.272 --> 00:25:41.305
- Hey, rookie!
- Yes.

00:25:41.305 --> 00:25:42.772
Go get the missing persons list, now.

00:25:42.772 --> 00:25:43.772
- Yes, sir.
- Hurry up!

00:25:43.772 --> 00:25:45.405
Yes!

00:25:50.867 --> 00:25:52.538
[Investigation Division]

00:25:52.538 --> 00:25:54.772
I checked all recent missing persons cases.

00:25:54.772 --> 00:25:57.938
These three are the only ones that match.

00:25:57.938 --> 00:26:01.072
[Missing Person Report]

00:26:04.372 --> 00:26:06.872
This victim's build is larger
than the suspect's.

00:26:06.872 --> 00:26:08.572
He wouldn't have attacked recklessly.

00:26:08.572 --> 00:26:10.605
He might've mistaken her for a man too.

00:26:10.605 --> 00:26:14.005
Then it's one of these two.

00:26:14.005 --> 00:26:15.241
Tae Joo,

00:26:15.241 --> 00:26:16.538
who do you think it is?

00:26:16.538 --> 00:26:18.572
What exactly is going on here?

00:26:18.572 --> 00:26:20.538
Sir, you're here.

00:26:21.672 --> 00:26:26.572
I clearly told you to exclude Detective Kang
from all investigations.

00:26:26.572 --> 00:26:29.172
- Are you taking my words lightly?
- There's been

00:26:29.172 --> 00:26:31.272
another serial murder case.

00:26:32.305 --> 00:26:35.472
Couldn't think of a better excuse,
so you came up with that?

00:26:36.705 --> 00:26:38.185
Why?

00:26:38.185 --> 00:26:40.638
Did a body turn up somewhere?

00:26:40.638 --> 00:26:43.105
The suspect said it himself.

00:26:43.105 --> 00:26:45.672
He claimed he's committed five murders.

00:26:46.405 --> 00:26:48.201
It could be

00:26:48.201 --> 00:26:50.438
a lie or an exaggeration.

00:26:50.438 --> 00:26:53.205
Now you're seriously going to
let the suspect to play you?

00:26:53.205 --> 00:26:55.372
But we still have to look into it!

00:26:56.272 --> 00:26:57.305
We're the police!

00:26:57.305 --> 00:27:01.805
And what if you really end up getting played?

00:27:05.705 --> 00:27:07.497
Then

00:27:07.497 --> 00:27:09.505
I'll take responsibility.

00:27:11.338 --> 00:27:13.838
Of course, you'll take responsibility.

00:27:24.472 --> 00:27:27.672
Apologize to Jeon Kyeong Ho
and reach a settlement.

00:27:27.672 --> 00:27:29.938
Then I'll let you back in.

00:27:29.938 --> 00:27:34.438
Assault is prosecuted upon complaint,
so no complaint, no charges.

00:27:38.605 --> 00:27:41.405
I think I'm being pretty generous.

00:27:41.405 --> 00:27:44.005
Yeah, Detective Kang, just apologize.

00:27:44.005 --> 00:27:46.105
Sir, just...

00:27:49.038 --> 00:27:50.938
Tae Joo.

00:27:50.938 --> 00:27:52.672
Even if it's unfair, what can we do?

00:27:52.672 --> 00:27:54.605
Let's catch the killer first.

00:28:01.605 --> 00:28:03.465
So?

00:28:03.465 --> 00:28:05.805
You're going to apologize, right?

00:28:08.672 --> 00:28:10.305
No.

00:28:12.238 --> 00:28:14.638
Detective Kang.

00:28:16.272 --> 00:28:19.972
Jeez, you always take
the hard way for no reason.

00:28:20.705 --> 00:28:23.372
Let me make a proposal this time.

00:28:25.138 --> 00:28:27.838
If you let me handle the search,

00:28:27.838 --> 00:28:31.838
I'll resign regardless of the outcome.

00:28:31.838 --> 00:28:33.805
I'll submit to an investigation too.

00:28:35.105 --> 00:28:36.872
About the search operation,

00:28:36.872 --> 00:28:38.672
as you said, Prosecutor,

00:28:38.672 --> 00:28:42.938
if nothing turns up, the police
and prosecution will look like fools again.

00:28:42.938 --> 00:28:44.805
If nothing comes up,

00:28:44.805 --> 00:28:48.038
just pin it all on the guy
who's quitting anyway.

00:28:50.672 --> 00:28:54.072
If I'm a card you're throwing away,
make full use of me.

00:28:56.305 --> 00:28:57.905
So be it.

00:29:01.938 --> 00:29:04.472
Let's wrap it up that way, Mr. Cha.

00:29:12.649 --> 00:29:15.305
[Muwon District Prosecutors' Office,
Kangseng Branch]

00:29:55.744 --> 00:29:57.155
[Missing Person Report]

00:29:59.683 --> 00:30:01.955
[Potential Crime Scene
in the Choi In Sook Case]

00:30:03.772 --> 00:30:06.305
It's Choi In Sook.

00:30:06.305 --> 00:30:07.872
Are you sure?

00:30:07.872 --> 00:30:09.638
Yes, I'm sure.

00:30:12.838 --> 00:30:14.605
If it's Choi In Sook,
that's the third murder.

00:30:14.605 --> 00:30:17.705
Based on both the date
of the disappearance and the location,

00:30:17.705 --> 00:30:19.905
it fits the suspect's pattern more.

00:30:20.572 --> 00:30:22.172
I'm sure of it.

00:30:22.805 --> 00:30:24.605
Choi In Sook.

00:30:35.738 --> 00:30:37.372
Hello?

00:30:43.705 --> 00:30:45.338
Is anyone here?

00:30:53.172 --> 00:30:54.772
Anyone home?

00:30:55.772 --> 00:30:57.372
Who is it?

00:30:58.638 --> 00:31:00.238
Is that you, In Sook?

00:31:06.838 --> 00:31:11.205
That darn girl, so despicable.

00:31:11.205 --> 00:31:15.138
Leaving her sick mother and running off?
How could you call that human?

00:31:15.138 --> 00:31:16.938
She'll be punished by heaven!

00:31:16.938 --> 00:31:18.472
I must've been out of my darn mind,

00:31:18.472 --> 00:31:22.672
giving birth to a girl like that
and even celebrating it.

00:31:23.305 --> 00:31:27.605
Did your daughter say anything when she left?

00:31:28.438 --> 00:31:32.405
She said she was going
into town to buy me clothes.

00:31:32.405 --> 00:31:34.438
She could talk a good game.

00:31:39.772 --> 00:31:44.233
What does someone
who stays home all day need clothes for?

00:31:44.233 --> 00:31:47.172
Isn't that just an excuse to run away?

00:31:47.172 --> 00:31:48.872
That nonsense again!

00:31:48.872 --> 00:31:51.772
Why would I leave home?

00:31:51.772 --> 00:31:56.372
I know you're praying for me to die
as soon as possible.

00:31:56.372 --> 00:31:58.172
I know it all!

00:31:58.172 --> 00:32:02.038
It's getting cold soon.
You'll get sick if you don't bundle up.

00:32:02.038 --> 00:32:05.072
I'll just buy some clothes
and come right back, okay?

00:32:05.072 --> 00:32:08.472
Darn it, come home or don't, I don't care.

00:32:08.472 --> 00:32:12.472
Since I'm buying,
I might as well pick a nice one.

00:32:25.005 --> 00:32:26.672
That darn girl.

00:32:28.072 --> 00:32:31.238
Do you really think your daughter ran away?

00:32:31.238 --> 00:32:35.705
That must be why she still hasn't come back.

00:32:35.705 --> 00:32:40.438
But why are you looking for her now?

00:32:40.438 --> 00:32:43.538
Are you afraid
she died some sudden, violent death?

00:32:43.538 --> 00:32:47.138
No way! I don't know about anything else,

00:32:47.138 --> 00:32:49.805
but she was supposed to live a long life.

00:32:49.805 --> 00:32:52.538
A fortune-telling monk said so.

00:32:59.405 --> 00:33:01.838
If she was coming back from the market,

00:33:01.838 --> 00:33:05.738
she'd get off there and take this road.

00:33:05.738 --> 00:33:09.638
From the bus stop
to Choi In Sook's house is roughly

00:33:09.638 --> 00:33:11.705
500 meters.

00:33:11.705 --> 00:33:14.972
So that means we have to
search this whole area, right?

00:33:14.972 --> 00:33:17.338
We'll need at least two squads.

00:33:20.472 --> 00:33:22.992
If something really turns up,

00:33:22.992 --> 00:33:24.972
what happens then?

00:33:27.672 --> 00:33:29.138
A search operation?

00:33:29.138 --> 00:33:30.805
[Muwon District Prosecutors' Office]
What are you doing right now?

00:33:30.805 --> 00:33:33.805
Why are you teaming up with him
instead of getting rid of him?

00:33:33.805 --> 00:33:36.438
It's a pretty credible tip.

00:33:36.438 --> 00:33:38.272
And if nothing turns up,

00:33:38.272 --> 00:33:40.705
someone needs to take responsibility.

00:33:40.705 --> 00:33:43.105
It won't be too late to remove him then.

00:33:43.105 --> 00:33:47.605
So you take the credit
and dump the blame on someone else?

00:33:52.572 --> 00:33:54.249
By the way,

00:33:54.249 --> 00:33:56.405
you and Kang Tae Joo were classmates, right?

00:33:56.405 --> 00:33:58.672
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:34:00.305 --> 00:34:02.153
Being classmates

00:34:02.153 --> 00:34:05.772
doesn't mean the law bends for him, right?

00:34:13.638 --> 00:34:16.772
Isn't it nice to be outside after so long?

00:34:16.772 --> 00:34:20.805
The wheelchair is overkill.
I told you I can walk.

00:34:21.505 --> 00:34:23.905
Didn't you hear the doctor?

00:34:23.905 --> 00:34:26.738
You might feel dizzy after a while.

00:34:26.738 --> 00:34:29.305
What if you fall while walking?

00:34:29.305 --> 00:34:30.972
Jeez.

00:34:30.972 --> 00:34:33.905
How did we both end up
in the hospital like this?

00:34:33.905 --> 00:34:36.572
Jeon Kyeong Ho, or Jeon whatever...

00:34:36.572 --> 00:34:39.438
Just wait till I'm discharged.
I'll deal with him!

00:34:39.438 --> 00:34:41.672
Still, I like being here with you.

00:34:41.672 --> 00:34:43.238
It's nice taking walks together like this.

00:34:43.238 --> 00:34:45.405
What's so good about it?

00:34:45.405 --> 00:34:48.905
Look, we're the only patients
out here by ourselves.

00:34:50.005 --> 00:34:53.872
What can we do? Neither of us has a guardian.

00:34:53.872 --> 00:34:57.738
What do you mean? You've got your brother.

00:34:57.738 --> 00:34:59.689
I guess

00:34:59.689 --> 00:35:01.405
he's ashamed of me.

00:35:01.405 --> 00:35:03.138
He doesn't even visit.

00:35:06.805 --> 00:35:09.605
Didn't you hear?

00:35:14.605 --> 00:35:18.838
Your brother beat Jeon Kyeong Ho up badly.

00:35:18.838 --> 00:35:20.009
[Police officer arrested]
Still, he's going through a rough time

00:35:20.009 --> 00:35:21.972
[for assaulting an active teacher]
because of it.

00:35:23.138 --> 00:35:24.937
But

00:35:24.937 --> 00:35:27.305
he's not going to
get in serious trouble over this, is he?

00:35:27.305 --> 00:35:30.605
I didn't want to tell you
because I knew you'd worry.

00:35:30.605 --> 00:35:33.338
But I figured you should know.

00:35:34.005 --> 00:35:37.938
Your brother really cares about you

00:35:37.938 --> 00:35:40.005
so much.

00:36:03.738 --> 00:36:06.838
Where did you wander off to?
You're a patient.

00:36:07.738 --> 00:36:11.838
What brings you to me first
instead of Ji Won?

00:36:11.838 --> 00:36:14.172
How's Ji Won?

00:36:14.172 --> 00:36:16.538
If you're curious, go see her yourself.

00:36:21.738 --> 00:36:23.672
You know you're getting
discharged tomorrow, right?

00:36:23.672 --> 00:36:24.838
I'll be here on time.

00:36:24.838 --> 00:36:27.305
You're leaving already?

00:36:27.305 --> 00:36:30.105
Why? Got something to say?

00:36:31.738 --> 00:36:33.638
Tae Joo, you know...

00:36:39.738 --> 00:36:41.372
See you tomorrow.

00:36:45.905 --> 00:36:47.572
Who are you?

00:36:49.172 --> 00:36:50.838
Hey, don't you recognize me?

00:36:50.838 --> 00:36:52.472
Seo Ji...

00:36:53.805 --> 00:36:55.672
Wait, you guys said she was fine, but why...

00:36:55.672 --> 00:36:57.305
You!

00:36:58.238 --> 00:37:00.772
Are you really the Kang Tae Joo I knew?

00:37:00.772 --> 00:37:03.405
How could you lose the suspect!

00:37:03.405 --> 00:37:05.638
And why are you resigning?

00:37:05.638 --> 00:37:07.905
Well, even if I did sleep a little,

00:37:07.905 --> 00:37:11.772
what is all this?

00:37:11.772 --> 00:37:13.305
"Slept a little"?

00:37:13.305 --> 00:37:17.672
Wow, Seo Ji Won, awesome! You're back.

00:37:17.672 --> 00:37:20.038
There might still be a way.

00:37:20.038 --> 00:37:21.038
What way?

00:37:21.038 --> 00:37:22.948
Well,

00:37:22.948 --> 00:37:24.972
I'll let you know when I'm certain.

00:37:24.972 --> 00:37:29.838
I'm going to help you catch the suspect,
so just wait.

00:37:31.105 --> 00:37:33.005
I'm going to take a break for now.

00:37:33.672 --> 00:37:36.305
- Then what about the suspect?
- Am I the only cop?

00:37:36.305 --> 00:37:37.972
They'll catch him.

00:37:40.972 --> 00:37:42.905
You're not Kang Tae Joo, are you?

00:37:43.738 --> 00:37:46.905
Well, I'm just a little tired.

00:37:46.905 --> 00:37:49.205
Maybe because I'm getting old.

00:37:49.205 --> 00:37:51.238
You should stop doing dangerous stuff too.

00:37:51.238 --> 00:37:53.805
You really... You almost died this time!

00:37:53.805 --> 00:37:55.472
Why?

00:37:55.472 --> 00:37:58.705
You won't get hit in the head
all the time if I'm not around, right?

00:38:02.705 --> 00:38:04.305
Why?

00:38:05.372 --> 00:38:06.972
What?

00:38:08.972 --> 00:38:10.605
Knock some sense into me sometimes!

00:38:11.472 --> 00:38:13.738
Keep me on my toes.

00:38:13.738 --> 00:38:15.972
You're the only one who can do that.

00:38:44.393 --> 00:38:45.897
[Seo Ji Won]

00:39:43.139 --> 00:39:44.737
Who's there!

00:39:44.737 --> 00:39:46.124
Jeez!

00:39:49.805 --> 00:39:51.905
You punk!

00:39:51.905 --> 00:39:53.838
You startled me!

00:39:53.838 --> 00:39:56.705
I almost died!

00:39:56.705 --> 00:39:59.172
Then why did you sneak in like a thief?

00:39:59.172 --> 00:40:01.572
I thought you might be sleeping.

00:40:03.705 --> 00:40:05.672
What is it at this hour?

00:40:06.305 --> 00:40:07.838
Did you find the camera?

00:40:07.838 --> 00:40:10.772
- No.
- Still not?

00:40:10.772 --> 00:40:13.605
Anyway, this came to the newsroom.

00:40:14.805 --> 00:40:16.038
It seemed urgent.

00:40:16.038 --> 00:40:18.072
[For Reporter Seo Ji Won, deliver by today
From Tae Joo's friend]

00:40:20.472 --> 00:40:23.438
"Deliver by today, from Tae Joo's friend."

00:40:53.038 --> 00:40:55.438
What's this? It's not even an arrest.

00:40:55.438 --> 00:40:57.172
Whether a body is found or not,

00:40:57.172 --> 00:41:01.005
today will probably be
the last time we see each other.

00:41:01.005 --> 00:41:02.138
Are you satisfied now?

00:41:02.138 --> 00:41:04.072
Things turned out the way you wanted.

00:41:04.072 --> 00:41:07.172
- The way I wanted?
- You don't have to see my face anymore.

00:41:11.072 --> 00:41:13.438
Any last words?

00:41:15.505 --> 00:41:17.938
Make sure to catch that punk.

00:41:17.938 --> 00:41:20.005
I heard you're quite a capable prosecutor.

00:41:20.005 --> 00:41:24.138
I don't care if you get promoted
or become famous because of this case.

00:41:24.138 --> 00:41:27.338
Just catch that punk
before he kills more people.

00:41:32.738 --> 00:41:36.105
You haven't seen today's paper yet, have you?

00:41:36.105 --> 00:41:37.772
Read it.

00:41:38.938 --> 00:41:40.538
There.

00:41:44.738 --> 00:41:47.405
[Controversy over fairness due to
close friendship with the prosecutor]

00:41:47.405 --> 00:41:50.672
"Controversy over fairness
due to close friendship

00:41:50.672 --> 00:41:53.272
with the prosecutor."

00:41:53.972 --> 00:41:56.238
What kind of nonsense is this?

00:41:57.538 --> 00:42:00.938
So this is how we become friends?

00:42:03.038 --> 00:42:04.638
My friend!

00:42:09.838 --> 00:42:14.851
Now that things have come to this,
we really need to close your assault case.

00:42:14.851 --> 00:42:17.405
It's them!

00:42:17.405 --> 00:42:19.038
Making a big show of it?

00:42:19.038 --> 00:42:21.805
That way, rumors will spread
that we cut ties.

00:42:23.572 --> 00:42:26.072
Why didn't you indict Sergeant Kang Tae Joo?

00:42:26.072 --> 00:42:28.238
- Did your friendship play a part?
- Watch your expression when you get out.

00:42:28.238 --> 00:42:30.072
Act like my close friend.

00:42:30.072 --> 00:42:33.105
Just let me finish the search operation.

00:42:33.105 --> 00:42:34.372
Why should I?

00:42:34.372 --> 00:42:37.338
I don't see any reason to cut you some slack.

00:42:37.338 --> 00:42:39.505
I want to find her daughter.

00:42:39.505 --> 00:42:41.272
For Ms. Choi In Sook's mother.

00:42:43.005 --> 00:42:44.105
Huh?

00:42:44.105 --> 00:42:45.705
Isn't that Governor Jeon Tae Geun?

00:42:45.705 --> 00:42:48.105
Yes. Go take a picture!

00:42:49.072 --> 00:42:50.772
What's going on?

00:42:54.772 --> 00:42:56.338
Governor, please say a few words.

00:42:56.338 --> 00:42:57.705
Please say a few words.

00:42:57.705 --> 00:42:59.538
How do you feel?

00:42:59.538 --> 00:43:01.705
Could you please say something?

00:43:03.472 --> 00:43:06.138
How is your condition?

00:43:06.138 --> 00:43:08.438
As someone holding public office,

00:43:08.438 --> 00:43:10.905
I stayed silent until now
about my own family's matter,

00:43:10.905 --> 00:43:13.205
- fearing it might look like outside pressure.
- What a show he's putting on.

00:43:13.205 --> 00:43:15.538
But I can't stand this anymore.

00:43:15.538 --> 00:43:17.838
Look at my nephew here!

00:43:17.838 --> 00:43:20.438
He can't even move around properly
on his own.

00:43:20.438 --> 00:43:21.972
Right there!

00:43:21.972 --> 00:43:24.638
It's all because he was assaulted
by that police officer!

00:43:24.638 --> 00:43:28.138
And yet, how is it that a cop
who assaulted an innocent citizen

00:43:28.138 --> 00:43:30.338
faces no punishment whatsoever?

00:43:30.338 --> 00:43:31.572
It's unfair!

00:43:31.572 --> 00:43:34.138
I need a full eight weeks to recover.

00:43:34.138 --> 00:43:38.038
My students are looking for me
at school, but I can't go to them.

00:43:38.038 --> 00:43:40.805
Is this how the police behave?
Is this acceptable?

00:43:40.805 --> 00:43:43.972
I said I'd report in for questioning
after today's search is done!

00:43:43.972 --> 00:43:45.838
Why are you doing that?

00:43:45.838 --> 00:43:48.405
Are you the only cop in Korea?

00:43:48.405 --> 00:43:51.905
What are you doing? Why aren't you
arresting that violent cop right now?

00:43:51.905 --> 00:43:53.449
Yes!

00:43:54.985 --> 00:43:56.538
What is that?

00:43:56.538 --> 00:43:59.005
Kyeong Ho, are you really
on an eight-week recovery?

00:43:59.005 --> 00:44:01.105
Wait, is it even okay for you
to drink like this?

00:44:01.105 --> 00:44:02.705
Eight weeks? What nonsense!

00:44:02.705 --> 00:44:05.672
Getting the medical report isn't hard at all.

00:44:05.672 --> 00:44:10.105
I spent some money
to screw that detective over!

00:44:11.972 --> 00:44:15.182
You should've just done your usual nonsense.

00:44:15.182 --> 00:44:17.005
Why mess with a teacher?

00:44:17.005 --> 00:44:20.138
Mess with her? I didn't even touch her.

00:44:20.138 --> 00:44:23.072
She caught on first and came at me.

00:44:23.072 --> 00:44:24.905
Who does she think she is?

00:44:24.905 --> 00:44:28.605
Hey, is she that pretty?

00:44:31.038 --> 00:44:33.438
She looks

00:44:34.305 --> 00:44:36.705
even prettier than Miss Korea.

00:44:39.049 --> 00:44:40.265
No, no!

00:44:42.038 --> 00:44:44.005
- Hey! Turn that off now!
- He looks fine to me.

00:44:53.205 --> 00:44:54.805
Turn that off!

00:44:54.805 --> 00:44:56.905
What? Is he actually injured?

00:44:59.105 --> 00:45:01.905
It's a frame-up! This is fabricated!

00:45:01.905 --> 00:45:03.238
What exactly is fabricated?

00:45:03.238 --> 00:45:05.005
Let's get out of here quickly!

00:45:05.005 --> 00:45:07.405
Governor, please say a few words!

00:45:07.405 --> 00:45:09.538
Did you know about your nephew's crime?

00:45:09.538 --> 00:45:10.872
No, absolutely not!

00:45:10.872 --> 00:45:13.238
Have you ever pressured the investigation?

00:45:13.238 --> 00:45:16.672
A hostess' daughter
acting all high and mighty...

00:45:16.672 --> 00:45:18.238
- That punk!
- Tae Joo!

00:45:18.238 --> 00:45:19.905
Hey!

00:45:21.405 --> 00:45:23.405
Kang Tae Joo, you punk!

00:45:23.405 --> 00:45:25.672
Are you going to make the same mistake twice?

00:45:26.838 --> 00:45:29.138
You said you'd find Ms. Choi In Sook.

00:45:36.800 --> 00:45:38.218
He looks perfectly fine.

00:45:38.218 --> 00:45:40.072
He's perfectly fine. Please say a word.

00:45:40.072 --> 00:45:42.889
Mr. Jeon Kyeong Ho, please go now.

00:45:43.561 --> 00:45:44.872
Wait!

00:45:44.872 --> 00:45:47.872
Uncle, Uncle!

00:45:47.872 --> 00:45:49.505
We should go together...

00:45:59.905 --> 00:46:02.105
- So, what are we photographing?
- We'll begin the search operation.

00:46:02.105 --> 00:46:04.238
The search scene here.

00:46:05.172 --> 00:46:07.272
Do you really think we'll find anything here?

00:46:07.272 --> 00:46:08.872
Unfortunately, yes.

00:46:09.672 --> 00:46:12.005
Keep distance from the person
next to you and move slowly!

00:46:12.005 --> 00:46:13.005
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

00:46:13.005 --> 00:46:16.838
Don't just pass by the reeds, leaves,
or branches in the thicket.

00:46:16.838 --> 00:46:18.405
Examine them thoroughly! Got it?

00:46:18.405 --> 00:46:20.005
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

00:46:21.672 --> 00:46:25.705
Keep your distance! Move slowly!

00:46:25.705 --> 00:46:27.705
You're Prosecutor Cha Si Young, right?

00:46:27.705 --> 00:46:30.172
I'm Seo Ji Won, a reporter
from Kangseng Daily.

00:46:30.172 --> 00:46:33.005
You were impressive today.

00:46:34.338 --> 00:46:37.972
I received a tape from an anonymous tipster,

00:46:37.972 --> 00:46:40.338
but I have no idea who sent it.

00:46:41.672 --> 00:46:44.705
Was it you who called
Jeon Kyeong Ho and Governor Jeon?

00:46:45.605 --> 00:46:47.505
That was nothing.

00:46:48.505 --> 00:46:50.305
Kim, did you wash the car properly?

00:46:50.305 --> 00:46:52.438
Yes, I cleaned it thoroughly.

00:46:52.438 --> 00:46:55.272
Did you know Sergeant Kang Tae Joo
was deployed on the operation today?

00:46:55.272 --> 00:46:56.705
It seemed like a fairly important operation.

00:46:56.705 --> 00:46:59.638
If he makes a contribution,
he might avoid disciplinary action.

00:47:03.272 --> 00:47:07.772
Whoever that tipster was,
they probably expected

00:47:07.772 --> 00:47:10.805
that you would blow it wide open, Ms. Seo.

00:47:15.705 --> 00:47:17.705
I didn't know you were classmates
with Detective Kang.

00:47:17.705 --> 00:47:19.505
You must have been quite close, huh?

00:47:21.472 --> 00:47:25.672
I had the chance to get close,
but I missed it.

00:47:25.672 --> 00:47:29.161
I heard you're close with Detective Kang.
How did you become friends?

00:47:30.605 --> 00:47:35.438
Well, we grew up in the same neighborhood
since we were kids.

00:47:35.438 --> 00:47:37.272
Since you were kids?

00:47:38.505 --> 00:47:40.605
Am I already too late?

00:47:45.505 --> 00:47:47.205
I found something.

00:47:47.205 --> 00:47:48.938
Where?

00:47:48.938 --> 00:47:50.738
Over here! This way!

00:48:07.605 --> 00:48:09.638
Preserve the scene.

00:48:09.638 --> 00:48:11.472
And call the forensics team.

00:48:34.872 --> 00:48:38.605
[Choi In Sook]

00:48:54.905 --> 00:48:57.638
You finally came back, my girl.

00:48:59.505 --> 00:49:01.505
You must've suffered.

00:49:03.705 --> 00:49:07.872
How wronged you must
have felt all this time...

00:49:09.105 --> 00:49:12.572
I didn't know I was running late.

00:49:13.672 --> 00:49:17.805
And I just kept scolding you for being late.

00:49:19.238 --> 00:49:21.105
I was wrong,

00:49:23.872 --> 00:49:25.538
my baby.

00:49:29.405 --> 00:49:33.372
Don't go anywhere anymore.

00:49:33.372 --> 00:49:35.938
Stay with me.

00:49:41.272 --> 00:49:42.872
Mom.

00:49:43.572 --> 00:49:45.438
Have you been well?

00:49:47.038 --> 00:49:49.005
I missed you.

00:51:09.405 --> 00:51:13.338
[Kangseng Daily]

00:51:13.338 --> 00:51:16.705
I'm back.

00:51:18.838 --> 00:51:20.038
What is it?

00:51:20.038 --> 00:51:23.938
Ms. Seo found the film
with the Kangseng serial killer on it.

00:51:23.938 --> 00:51:25.938
- What?
- It's being developed now.

00:51:25.938 --> 00:51:28.772
Isn't that the biggest scoop?

00:51:28.772 --> 00:51:31.305
But I don't think
the photo will come out alright.

00:51:31.305 --> 00:51:34.205
Don't jinx it. Shut up!

00:51:37.038 --> 00:51:38.438
[Film in development
When light is on, no entry]

00:51:38.438 --> 00:51:40.505
Oh, it came out. It came out.

00:51:42.272 --> 00:51:43.905
It came out?

00:51:56.572 --> 00:51:57.572
Thanks for the meal!

00:51:57.572 --> 00:52:01.138
Eat up. It's an extra-large special,
on the house today.

00:52:01.138 --> 00:52:03.905
What's gotten into you? You're usually
strict about paying even with friends.

00:52:03.905 --> 00:52:07.272
You must've had a really hard time
because of Sun Young.

00:52:07.272 --> 00:52:11.238
Now that Sun Young's cleared her name
and the scandal's all gone...

00:52:11.238 --> 00:52:13.172
What are you talking about?

00:52:13.172 --> 00:52:15.372
You really didn't know anything?

00:52:15.372 --> 00:52:18.738
It was even on the front page
that Tae Joo beat that guy up.

00:52:18.738 --> 00:52:20.372
It's probably that guy.

00:52:20.372 --> 00:52:23.138
The one who took Sun Young in a Grandeur.

00:52:42.905 --> 00:52:44.538
Ki Beom...

00:52:55.305 --> 00:52:57.238
Why didn't you tell me?

00:52:59.972 --> 00:53:02.772
Even if no one else knows, I should've known.

00:53:02.772 --> 00:53:06.305
I'm your groom, and you're my bride!

00:53:09.138 --> 00:53:11.905
- Ki Beom...
- Where is that punk now?

00:53:14.405 --> 00:53:16.105
Let's break up.

00:53:18.105 --> 00:53:19.738
What?

00:53:24.572 --> 00:53:26.505
Let's break up.

00:53:46.072 --> 00:53:47.405
You just got here,
and you're already leaving?

00:53:47.405 --> 00:53:49.172
Yes, I'm leaving.

00:53:49.172 --> 00:53:52.705
Take care. I won't walk you out.

00:53:52.705 --> 00:53:54.338
No need for that.

00:53:59.772 --> 00:54:02.238
I'll just leave after causing trouble, sir.

00:54:03.472 --> 00:54:05.262
You really worked hard.

00:54:05.262 --> 00:54:07.205
You've been through a lot.

00:54:54.305 --> 00:54:57.338
[Stepping away for a moment]

00:55:01.305 --> 00:55:03.505
My art tube...

00:55:13.472 --> 00:55:15.305
- Oh my!
- Uh, you scared me!

00:55:15.305 --> 00:55:17.872
You startled me!

00:55:17.872 --> 00:55:19.433
What are you doing?

00:55:19.433 --> 00:55:21.705
I left something behind.

00:55:21.705 --> 00:55:23.572
What about you, sir?

00:55:23.572 --> 00:55:24.705
What did you leave behind?

00:55:24.705 --> 00:55:26.172
My art tube.

00:55:26.172 --> 00:55:28.872
My drawings are in it.

00:55:28.872 --> 00:55:31.538
So why are you here?

00:55:31.538 --> 00:55:34.238
I'm friends with the owner.

00:55:34.238 --> 00:55:37.572
Huh? With Andy Lau?

00:55:38.238 --> 00:55:40.572
He's my friend's younger brother.

00:55:40.572 --> 00:55:43.372
Oh, okay.

00:55:43.372 --> 00:55:46.505
Your tone is a bit off.

00:55:46.505 --> 00:55:48.272
Don't you have a killer to catch?

00:55:48.272 --> 00:55:50.205
When are you ever going to
catch him at this rate?

00:55:50.205 --> 00:55:52.805
Why does everyone bring up the killer
whenever they see me?

00:55:52.805 --> 00:55:54.409
Well...

00:55:54.409 --> 00:55:57.172
I'm not a cop anymore. I quit.

00:55:57.905 --> 00:56:01.005
Then what about the killer?

00:56:01.005 --> 00:56:03.072
The other police officers will...

00:56:03.705 --> 00:56:05.805
You just focus on your studies.

00:56:05.805 --> 00:56:08.272
Go home early, and...

00:56:09.438 --> 00:56:13.538
If you see anything like a scarecrow
at night, just run, okay?

00:56:13.538 --> 00:56:15.338
Why?

00:56:15.338 --> 00:56:18.072
Because it might not actually be a scarecrow.

00:56:18.072 --> 00:56:19.938
Remember what I said.

00:56:21.205 --> 00:56:22.805
Why aren't you answering?

00:56:23.472 --> 00:56:25.338
Well...

00:56:25.338 --> 00:56:28.705
Can't you not quit being a cop?

00:56:28.705 --> 00:56:32.138
I want you to catch him yourself, sir.

00:56:34.972 --> 00:56:36.272
Oh, this is just, well...

00:56:36.272 --> 00:56:37.338
Jeez.

00:56:37.338 --> 00:56:39.238
If only grown-ups' business

00:56:39.238 --> 00:56:42.872
were as simple as flipping pancakes...

00:56:45.005 --> 00:56:46.772
What's this?

00:56:46.772 --> 00:56:48.338
It's a bribe.

00:56:48.338 --> 00:56:52.572
When you eat it,
just think it over twice more, okay?

00:56:52.572 --> 00:56:54.205
Bye!

00:56:55.772 --> 00:56:59.938
Giving a bribe to a guy who got fired?
What a waste.

00:57:19.172 --> 00:57:20.905
Stop staring at it, okay?

00:57:20.905 --> 00:57:23.338
Do you think staring
will bring back your focus?

00:57:23.338 --> 00:57:27.305
Jeez, I thought we finally
got a real scoop this time.

00:57:28.772 --> 00:57:30.572
Let's run it as is.

00:57:30.572 --> 00:57:31.638
As is?

00:57:31.638 --> 00:57:33.638
I can't even make out the eyes,
nose, or mouth.

00:57:33.638 --> 00:57:35.905
You never know. Someone might recognize him.

00:57:35.905 --> 00:57:38.605
No way.

00:57:38.605 --> 00:57:41.238
At least one person will!
The suspect himself.

00:57:41.238 --> 00:57:45.638
Even if it doesn't identify him,
it can still pressure the suspect.

00:57:45.638 --> 00:57:48.272
"You've been caught on camera."

00:57:51.838 --> 00:57:53.772
Let's break up.

00:57:54.905 --> 00:57:56.838
Ki Beom!

00:57:56.838 --> 00:57:58.572
Ki Beom, are you okay?

00:57:58.572 --> 00:58:00.205
Stop it.

00:58:00.972 --> 00:58:03.572
What's wrong with you today?

00:58:03.572 --> 00:58:04.672
Hey.

00:58:04.672 --> 00:58:06.738
If you're tired, go home first.
I'll handle it.

00:58:06.738 --> 00:58:07.838
No, we have a lot to tidy up.

00:58:07.838 --> 00:58:10.972
Go home first.
We're almost at closing time anyway.

00:58:10.972 --> 00:58:13.772
- I'll do it.
- Jeez, just listen to me.

00:58:17.572 --> 00:58:20.105
Excuse me.

00:58:25.205 --> 00:58:26.438
Is this yours?

00:58:26.438 --> 00:58:29.272
Yes, thank you.

00:58:29.272 --> 00:58:32.305
It's late. Do you think
you can go by yourself?

00:58:32.305 --> 00:58:35.438
I'm fine. It's just a quick bus ride.

00:58:35.438 --> 00:58:37.638
Goodbye.

00:58:37.638 --> 00:58:39.472
Goodbye.

00:58:45.205 --> 00:58:49.872
She should've gone home earlier.
It's really dangerous these days.

00:58:51.505 --> 00:58:54.205
Huh? It's raining.

00:59:03.372 --> 00:59:05.905
What? It's a scarecrow.

00:59:06.538 --> 00:59:09.705
If you see anything
like a scarecrow at night, just run.

00:59:10.905 --> 00:59:13.338
Because it might not actually be a scarecrow.

01:00:44.738 --> 01:00:45.772
Yes, hello?

01:00:45.772 --> 01:00:47.005
Sir.

01:00:47.005 --> 01:00:50.172
Well, a body...

01:00:50.172 --> 01:00:51.838
It's another murder.

01:00:55.505 --> 01:00:57.438
Why are you telling me this?

01:00:58.072 --> 01:01:00.972
Did you forget I quit? I'm hanging up.

01:01:00.972 --> 01:01:02.672
The dead girl

01:01:04.805 --> 01:01:06.505
is Min Ji.

01:01:09.072 --> 01:01:10.705
Who?

01:01:13.438 --> 01:01:15.605
Kang Tae Joo!

01:01:15.605 --> 01:01:18.405
- Hey, you...
- Why are you here?

01:01:18.405 --> 01:01:20.005
Hey!

01:01:20.005 --> 01:01:21.438
Kang Tae Joo!

01:01:21.438 --> 01:01:23.338
Sir.

01:01:23.338 --> 01:01:25.538
- Hey, stop him! Keep him away!
- Block him, you punks!

01:01:25.538 --> 01:01:26.605
- Keep him away! Block him!
- Sir.

01:01:26.605 --> 01:01:29.105
- Kang Tae Joo!
- Hey, stop him!

01:01:29.772 --> 01:01:30.905
Hey, you punk!

01:01:30.905 --> 01:01:31.905
Hey, you!

01:01:31.905 --> 01:01:34.272
What are you doing here?

01:01:34.272 --> 01:01:35.905
Kang Tae Joo.

01:02:05.172 --> 01:02:09.372
[Kim Min Ji]

01:02:27.811 --> 01:02:29.305
We said we'd handle it.

01:02:29.305 --> 01:02:32.297
What are you doing here? Go! We'll handle it.

01:02:33.187 --> 01:02:35.105
You really need to leave.

01:02:35.105 --> 01:02:37.449
So why did you...

01:02:37.449 --> 01:02:41.272
Hey, your nose is bleeding.

01:02:42.019 --> 01:02:44.672
What's going on with you?

01:02:44.672 --> 01:02:45.705
Kang Tae Joo!

01:02:45.705 --> 01:02:47.305
Hey!

01:02:48.163 --> 01:02:49.449
Kang Tae Joo!

01:02:50.105 --> 01:02:51.905
Kang Tae Joo!

01:02:51.905 --> 01:02:52.905
Take him away, now.

01:02:52.905 --> 01:02:54.538
Kang Tae Joo!

01:02:54.538 --> 01:02:56.759
Someone get him out of here!

01:02:56.759 --> 01:02:59.105
Hey, bring a stretcher.

01:02:59.105 --> 01:03:02.172
A life's mission?

01:03:02.172 --> 01:03:06.038
How did you end up getting into that,

01:03:06.038 --> 01:03:08.238
your life's mission?

01:03:09.105 --> 01:03:10.772
It might have started

01:03:13.072 --> 01:03:15.538
that day, I guess.

01:03:21.305 --> 01:03:24.005
This time, I'll be the one asking.

01:03:24.638 --> 01:03:29.072
Was it you who ruined my mission,
Mr. Lee Yong Woo?

01:03:35.605 --> 01:03:37.338
Mr. Lee Yong Woo.

01:03:44.638 --> 01:03:46.738
Oh, come on.

01:03:46.738 --> 01:03:51.305
Repeating the same thing isn't fun.

01:03:51.305 --> 01:03:53.305
Alright.

01:03:53.305 --> 01:03:58.105
Since it's something I did anyway,
I'll lay it all out.

01:03:58.105 --> 01:03:59.705
Are you saying you'll confess?

01:03:59.705 --> 01:04:02.072
It's going to be a pretty long story.

01:04:02.072 --> 01:04:05.072
You've got enough time, right?

01:04:05.072 --> 01:04:06.972
Of course.

01:04:12.738 --> 01:04:14.972
Where should we start?

01:04:14.972 --> 01:04:16.905
But

01:04:16.905 --> 01:04:19.238
please tell me your story too.

01:04:19.238 --> 01:04:21.638
It's no fun if I'm the only one talking.

01:04:21.638 --> 01:04:23.272
You tell yours,

01:04:23.272 --> 01:04:25.038
and I'll tell mine.

01:04:25.038 --> 01:04:26.601
That way,

01:04:26.601 --> 01:04:29.672
we can complete our story.

01:04:32.338 --> 01:04:34.038
"Our story"?

01:04:34.038 --> 01:04:36.138
Yes.

01:04:36.138 --> 01:04:37.738
Ours.

01:05:14.372 --> 01:05:16.172
I've got to catch that punk.

01:05:16.172 --> 01:05:17.605
Let's catch him together.

01:05:17.605 --> 01:05:19.338
[National Saemaeul Leaders Convention]
So that's why you came back?

01:05:19.338 --> 01:05:20.905
Unbelievable, Seo Ji Won.

01:05:20.905 --> 01:05:22.972
We didn't even see a strand of his hair.

01:05:22.972 --> 01:05:24.505
Does that make any sense?

01:05:24.505 --> 01:05:26.772
You don't even know
what kind of woman she is, do you?

01:05:26.772 --> 01:05:30.205
- You're being fooled too.
- I said shut up!

01:05:30.205 --> 01:05:32.705
Jeon Kyeong Ho again? Seriously?

01:05:32.705 --> 01:05:36.338
Thinking back now, it was all bait.

01:05:37.305 --> 01:05:39.505
Kang Sun Young!

01:05:39.505 --> 01:05:41.138
Who's there?